netistrar.clientapi.objects.domain

Class DomainNameTransferStatus

  • java.lang.Object
    • netistrar.clientapi.objects.domain.DomainNameTransferStatus

  • public class DomainNameTransferStatus
extends java.lang.Object
    This encodes details about a domain transfer. When a domain name is in the TRANSFER_IN_AWAITING_RESPONSE status this will be fully populated with details about the transfer window as obtained from the Registry.

    Otherwise if the domain name is in a pending confirmation status this will only have the domainName and status members set.
